sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant SQS
    participant Worker
    participant Bedrock
    participant EventBridge
    
    Client->>API: POST /async {doc}
    API->>SQS: SendMessage
    API-->>Client: 202 Accepted {jobId}
    
    SQS->>Worker: Consume Message
    Worker->>Bedrock: Generate Embeddings
    Bedrock-->>Worker: Vector
    Worker->>EventBridge: PutEvents(JobComplete)
